headline: Cognizant Doubles Down on Synapse Commitment with New Target to Reach Two Million by 2030
summary: Cognizant today announced an expansion of its Synapse initiative, setting a new goal to upskill a total of two million individuals by the end of 2030. Having already exceeded its original target of one million by the end of 2026 – Cognizant is doubling down on its commitment to empower individuals with the training they need to participate in tomorrow's digitally-driven workforce.
